name: AVCapturePhotoOutput.QualityPrioritization
desc: Constants that indicate how to prioritize photo quality relative to capture speed.

items.name: case speed
items.desc: Speed of photo delivery is most important, even at the expense of quality.

items.name: case quality
items.desc: Photo quality is most important, even at the expense of shot-to-shot time.

items.name: case balanced
items.desc: Priority is balanced between photo quality and speed of delivery.
